text: Brutally efficient warriors in life, these followers of the Dread King are the spearhead of his army in death.
Lured by promises of eternal unlife and power, Gunther Larenscheld has awoken the Dread King from his slumber and sworn loyalty to Nagash's cause.
Some Priests excel at manipulating the Wind of Shyish, and are unsurpassed at Death Magic.
The ancient Priests were masters of many forms of magic, the spells of shadows and illusion are no exception.
When they were corrupted by the Dread King, many Priests learned the dark arts of Necromancy.
A Hellwraith is a terrifying prospect that has no corporeal form, making it extremely difficult to kill with conventional weaponry.
